quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  15,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  15,1,Alif Laaam Raa ا. yeh khuda ki kitaab aur quran roshan ki ayatain hain
  15,2,kisi waqt kafir log arzoo karen ge ke ae kash woh musalman hotay
  15,3,( ae Mohammad ) un ko unn ke haal par rehne do ke khalin aur faiday athaliN aur ( tole ) Amal un ko duniya mein mashgool kiye rahay anqareeb un ko ( is ka injaam ) maloom ho jaye ga
  15,4,aur hum ne koi bastii halaak nahi ki. magar is ka waqt marqoom o moayan tha
  15,5,koi jamaat apni muddat ( wafaat ) se nah agay nikal sakti hai nah peechay reh sakti hai
  15,6,aur kufar kehte hain ke ae shakhs jis par nasiyaat ( ki kitaab ) nazil hui hai too to deewana hai
  15,7,agar to sacha hai to hamaray paas firshton ko kyun nahi le aata
  15,8,( keh do ) hum firshton ko nazil nahikiya karte magar haq ke sath aur is waqt un ko mohlat nahi millti
  15,9,be shak yeh ( kitaab ) nasiyaat hamein ne aُtari hai aur hum hi is ke nigehbaan hain
  15,10,aur hum ne tum se pehlay logon mein bhi paighambar beje they
  15,11,aur unn ke paas koi paighambar nahi aata tha magar woh uss ke sathistehzaa karte they
  15,12,isi terhan hum is ( takzib o zalal ) ko gunahgaaron ke dilon mein daakhil kar dete hain
  15,13,so woh is par imaan nahi laatay aur pehloo ki rawish bhi yahi rahi hai
  15,14,avragr hum aasman ka koi darwaaza unn par khol den aur woh is mein charhne bhi lagen
  15,15,to bhi yahi kahin ke hamari ankhen makhmoor hogayi hain balkay hum par jaadoo kar diya gaya hai
  15,16,aur hum hi ne aasman mein burj banaye aur dekhnay walon ke liye uss ko saja diya
  15,17,aur har shetan راندہٴ dargaah se ussay mehfooz kar diya
  15,18,haan agar koi chori se sunna chahay to chamakta howa angara is ke peechay lpkta hai
  15,19,aur zameen ko bhi hum hi ne phelaya aur is par pahar ( bana kar ) rakh diye aur is mein har aik sanjeeda cheez ugai
  15,20,aur hum hi ne tumahray liye aur un logon ke liye jin ko tum rozi nahi dete is mein muaash ke samaan peda kiye
  15,21,aur hamaray haan har cheez ke khazanay hain aur hum un ko بمقدار munhasib utaartay rehtay hain
  15,22,aur hum hi hawae chillate hain ( jo baadalon ke pani se ) bhari hui hoti hain aur hum hi aasman se meen barastee hain aur hum hi tum ko is ka pani pilate hain aur tum to is ka خرانہ nahi rakhtay
  15,23,aur hum hi hayaat bkhshte aur hum hi mout dete hain. aur hum sab ke waris ( maalik ) hain
  15,24,aur jo log tum mein pehlay guzar chuke hain hum ko maloom hain aur jo peechay anay walay hain woh bhi hum ko maloom hain
  15,25,aur tumhara perwar-digaar ( qayamat ke din ) un sab ko jama kere ga woh bara Dana ( aur ) khabardaar hai
  15,26,aur hum ne ensaan ko khankhnate sarray hue gaaray se pedakiya hai
  15,27,aur junoo ko is se bhi pehlay be dhowen ki aag se pedakiya tha
  15,28,aur jab tumahray perwar-digaar ne firshton se farmaya ke mein khankhnate srhe hue gaaray se aik bashar bananay wala hon
  15,29,jab is ko ( soorat ainsaniya mein ) durust kar lon aur is mein apni ( be baha cheez yani ) rooh phoonk dun to is ke agay sjday mein gir parna
  15,30,to farishtay to sab ke sab sjday mein gir parre
  15,31,magar shetan ke is ne sajda karne walon ke sath honay se inkaar kar diya
  15,32,( khuda ne farmaya ) ke iblees! tujhekiya howa ke to sajda karne walon mein shaamil nah howa
  15,33,( is ne ) kaha ke mein aisa nahi hon ke ensaan ko jis ko to ne khankhnate srhe hue gaaray se banaya hai sajda karoon
  15,34,( khuda ne ) farmaya yahan se nikal ja. to mardood hai
  15,35,aur tujh par qayamat ke din taq laanat ( barsay gi )
  15,36,( is ne ) kaha ke perwar-digaar mujhe is din taq mohlat day jab log ( marnay ke baad ) zindah kiye jayen ge
  15,37,farmaya ke tujhe mohlat di jati hai
  15,38,waqt muqarrar ( yani qayamat ) ke din taq
  15,39,( is ne ) kaha ke perwar-digaar jaissa tunay mujhe raste se allagkiya hai mein bhi zameen mein logon ke liye ( gunaaho ) ko aaraasta kar dukhao ga aur sab ko behkaon ga
  15,40,haan un mein jo tairay mukhlis bande hain ( un par qaboo chalna mushkil hai )
  15,41,( khuda ne ) farmaya ke mujh taq ( pounchanay ka ) yahi seedha rasta hai
  15,42,jo mere ( mukhlis ) bande hain un par tujhe kuch qudrat nahi ( ke un ko gunah mein daal sakay ) haan bad raahon mein se jo tairay peechay chal parre
  15,43,aur un sab ke waday ki jagah jahannum hai
  15,44,is ke saat darwazay hain. har aik darwazay ke liye un mein se jamaten taqseem kar di gayi hain
  15,45,jo mut-taqi hain woh baghoon aur chashmo mein hon ge
  15,46,( un se kaha jaye ga ke ) un mein salamti ( aur khatir jama se ) daakhil hojao
  15,47,aur un ke dilon mein jo kudorat hogi un ko hum nikaal kar ( saaf kar ) den ge ( goya ) bhai bhai takhton par aik dosray ke samnay baithy hue hain
  15,48,nah un ko wahan koi takleef puhanche gi aur nah wahan se nikalay jayen ge
  15,49,( ae paighambar ) mere bundon ko btado ke mein bara bakhsnay wala ( aur ) meharban hon
  15,50,aur yeh ke mera azaab bhi dard dainay wala azaab hai
  15,51,aur un ko ibrahim ke mehmanon ka ahwaal suna do
  15,52,jab woh ibrahim ke paas aeye to salam kaha. ( unhon ne ) kaha ke hamein to tum se dar lagta hai
  15,53,( mehmanon ne ) kaha ke daryay nahi hum aap ko aik danishmand larke ki khushkhabri dete hain
  15,54,bolay ke jab mujhe burhapay ne aa pakra to tum khushkhabri dainay lagey. ab kaahe ki khushkhabri dete ho
  15,55,( unhon ne ) kaha hum aap ko sachhi khushkhabri dete hain aap mayoos nah hoyie
  15,56,( ibrahim ne ) kaha ke khuda ki rehmat se ( mein mayoos kyun honay laga is se ) mayoos hona gumrahon ka kaam hai
  15,57,phir kehnay lagey ke farishto! tumhe ( aur )kiya kaam hai
  15,58,( unhon ne ) kaha ke hum aik gunehgaar qoum ki taraf beje gay hain ( ke is ko azaab karen )
  15,59,magar Loot ke ghar walay ke un sab ko hum bchalin ge
  15,60,Albata un ki aurat ( ke ) is ke liye hum ne thehra diya hai ke woh peechay reh jaye gi
  15,61,phir jab farishtay Loot ke ghar gay
  15,62,to Loot ne kaha tum to na aashna se log ho
  15,63,woh bolay ke nahi balkay hum aap ke paas woh cheez le kar aeye hain jis mein log shak karte they
  15,64,aur hum aap ke paas yakeeni baat le kar aeye hain aur hum sach kehte hain
  15,65,to aap kuch raat rahay se apne ghar walon ko le nikleen aur khud un ke peechay chalein aur aur aap mein se koi shakhs murr kar nah dekhe. aur jahan aap ko hukum ho wahan chalay jayye
  15,66,aur hum ne Loot ki taraf wahi bhaije ke un logon ki jarr subah hotay hotay kaat di jaye gi
  15,67,aur ahal shehar ( Loot ke paas ) khush khush ( doray ) aeye
  15,68,( Loot ne ) kaha ke yeh mere mehman hain ( kahin un ke baray mein ) mujhe ruswa nah karna
  15,69,aur khuda se daro. aur meri be aabrui nah ki jo
  15,70,woh bolaykiya hum ne tum ko saaray Jahan ( ki himayat o tarfdari ) se mana nahikiya
  15,71,( unhon ne ) kaha ke agar tumhe karna hi hai to yeh meri ( qoum ki ) larkiyan hain ( un se shadi karlo )
  15,72,( ae Mohammad ) tumhari jaan ki qasam woh apni masti mein madhosh ( ho rahay ) they
  15,73,so un ko Sooraj nikaltay nikaltay chngharh ne aapkrha
  15,74,aur hum ne is shehar ko ( ulat kar ) neechay oopar kardiya. aur un par khangar ki pathriyan barsaaen
  15,75,be shak is ( qissay ) mein ahal firasat ke liye nishani hai
  15,76,aur woh ( shehar ) ab taq seedhay raste par ( mojood ) hai
  15,77,be shak is mein imaan laane walon ke liye nishani hai
  15,78,aur ban ke rehne walay ( yani qoum Shoiab ke log ) bhi gunehgaar they
  15,79,to hum ne un se bhi badla liya. aur yeh dono shehar khulay raste par ( mojood ) hain
  15,80,aur ( waadi ) hijr ke rehne walon ne bhi payghambaroon ki takzieeb ki
  15,81,hum ne un ko apni nishanain den aur woh un se munh phirtay rahay
  15,82,aur woh pahoron ko taraash taraash kar ghar banatay they ( ke ) aman ( wa itmenaan ) se rahen ge
  15,83,to cheekh ne un ko subah hotay hotay aapkrha
  15,84,aur jo kaam woh karte they woh un ke kuch bhi kaam nah aeye
  15,85,aur hum ne asmano aur zameen ko aur jo ( makhloqaat ) un mein hai is ko tadbeer ke sath pedakiya hai. aur qayamat to zaroor aakar rahay gi to tum ( un logon se ) achi terhan se dar guzar karo
  15,86,kuch shak nahi ke tumhara perwar-digaar ( sab kuch ) peda karne wala ( aur ) jan-nay wala hai
  15,87,aur hum ne tum ko saat ( ayatain ) jo ( namaz mein ) dohra kar parhi jati hain ( yani سورہٴ alhmd ) aur Azmat wala quran ataa farmaya hai
  15,88,aur hum ne kufar ki kayi jamaaton ko jo ( fawaid dunyawi se ) mtmtakiya hai tum un ki taraf ( raghbat se ) aankhh utha kar nah dekhna aur nah un ke haal par tasuf karna aur mominoun se khatir aur tawaza se paish aana
  15,89,aur keh do ke mein to alania dar sunanay wala hon
  15,90,( aur hum un kufar par isi terhan azaab nazil karen ge ) jis terhan un logon par nazilkiya jinhon ne taqseem kardiya
  15,91,yani quran ko ( kuch maan-ne aur kuch nah maan-ne se ) tukre tukre kar dala
  15,92,tumahray perwar-digaar ki qasam hum un se zaroor prssh karen ge
  15,93,un kamon ki jo woh karte rahay
  15,94,pas jo hukum tum ko ( khuda ki taraf se ) mila hai woh ( logon ko ) suna do aur mushrikon ka ( zara ) khayaal nah karo
  15,95,hum tumhe un logon ( ke shar ) se bachanay ke liye jo tum seistehzaa karte hain kaafi hain
  15,96,jo khuda ke sath mabood qarar dete hain. so anqareeb un ko ( un baton ka injaam ) maloom hojaye ga
  15,97,aur hum jantay hain ke un baton se tumhara dil tang hota hai
  15,98,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki tasbeeh kehte aur ( is ki ) khoobiyan bayan karte raho aur sajda karne walon mein daakhil raho
  15,99,aur apne perwar-digaar ki ibadat kiye jao yahan taq ke tumhari mout ( ka waqt ) aajay
